{"word":"G922 - βάρος - báros - bar'-os - Burden","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">βάρος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>báros"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>bar'-os"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Burden"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"கஷ்டம், பாரம், உபத்திரவம் - பால்வேறுபாடற்ற பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"heaviness, weight, burden, trouble"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Probably from the same as <a href=\"#/G939 - βάσις - básis - bas'-ece/939\">G939</a> (through the notion of <i>going</i> down; compare <a href=\"#/G899 - βάθος - báthos - bath'-os/899\">G899</a>); <i>weight</i>; in the New Testament only, figuratively a <i>load</i>, <i>abundance</i>, <i>authority:</i> - burden (-some), weight."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G916 - βαρέω - baréō - bar-eh'-o/916\">G916</a>, <a href=\"#/G922 - βάρος - báros - bar'-os/922\">G922</a>, <a href=\"#/G926 - βαρύς - barýs - bar-ooce'/926\">G926</a>"}]}